Description: Welcome to Todo High, whose student body is composed of the toughest of brawlers.
Title: TENJO TENGE: FULL CONTACT EDITION, VOL. 3
Author: Oh!great

Description: Meet Black Jack, a surgeon roaming the globe and performing medical miracles. Too bad he does not have a license to practice.
Title: BLACK JACK, VOL. 16
Author: Osamu Tezuka

Description: All the students at St. Kleio Academy are clones of prominent historical figures. In this volume, Florence Nightingale gets the spotlight.
Title: AFTERSCHOOL CHARISMA, VOL. 4
Author: Kumiko Suekane

Description: The incredibly popular manga series that spawned an anime series, stage musicals and countless imitators gets a new printing.
Title: SAILOR MOON, VOL. 1
Author: Naoko Takeuchi

Description: Cross Academy has day and evening students, but the latter have a secret: they are vampires.
Title: VAMPIRE KNIGHT, VOL. 13
Author: Matsuri Hino

Description: Gon is the world’s last dinosaur. These are his adventures.
Title: GON, VOL. 2
Author: Masashi Tanaka

Description: Life in a high school filled with werewolves and vampires continues.
Title: ROSARIO+VAMPIRE: SEASON II, VOL. 6
Author: Akihisa Ikeda

Description: A manga store is the central setting for this series, which follows the trials and tribulations of the store’s customers.
Title: KINGYO USED BOOKS, VOL. 4
Author: Seimu Yoshizaki

Description: A predecessor to "Sailor Moon," this collection of stories has never before been printed in the United States.
Title: CODENAME: SAILOR V, Vol. 1
Author: Naoko Takeuchi

Description: Rin Okumura joins an exorcist academy in order to control his inner demon. Will his classmates find out about his satanic bloodline?
Title: BLUE EXORCIST, VOL. 4
Author: Kazue Kato
